   500вҶ’## Design considerations вҖҰ
   502вҶ’### Don't break anything
   504вҶ’Allow structured logging to be added in the current `0.4.x` series of `log`. This gives us the option of including structured logging in an `0.4.x` release, or bumping the minor crate version without introducing any actual breaking changes.
   505вҶ’
